  "To build a modern, interactive application, you’re going to need the ability to listen to and respond to events –&nbsp;obviously. Thankfully, the API to do this in React is fairly simple and it involves two things you’re already familiar with –&nbsp;props and functions.": "",
  "First, we'll start with a button element.": "",
